Enum Symbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Symbol>
      • core.Symbol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Symbol>

    public enum Symbol
extends java.lang.Enum<Symbol>
implements java.lang.Comparable<Symbol>
    Possible symbols of a card. The following is associated with each symbol:
    - strength: strength relative to other symbols (between 0 and 7)
    - value: amount of points the symbol is worth
    Author:
    Daan Seynaeve
